ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 1 TO THE SPECIES AT RISK ACT adds or reclassifies 31 species to the Schedule in order to help maintain Canada's biodiversity and the health and resilience of Canadian ecosystems by preventing wildlife species from being extirpated from Canada or becoming extinct and contributing to their recovery.
